  "text": "In the update environment we use only simple topological integrity constraints for driving the user in the update operations. Moreover, in this first version of the update environment we focus only on spatial objects of the domain Dpolygon and consequently also the spatial formula of TC(S) have been redefined to work only on polygons. In particular, the functional symbols b(s), f(s) and t(s) (with s spatial term) have been removed and the topological relations used in the spatial formulas sl L) s2 have been substituted by the topological relations for areal objects defined in [CITATION_1] with the Dimension Extended Method. We call this new set of relations Rel~ °ty.",
